UDP.name: UDP
UDP.stream_server: gst-launch-1.0 -v filesrc location="/home/matt/Documents/zoom_recording.mp4" ! qtdemux name=demux  demux.video_0  ! rtph264pay ! udpsink host={addr} port=5000
UDP.stream_client: gst-launch-1.0 udpsrc address={addr} port=5000 caps="application/x-rtp, media=(string)video, clock-rate=(int)90000, encoding-name=(string)H264, payload=(int)96" ! rtpjitterbuffer latency={buffer_delay} ! rtph264depay ! h264parse ! queue  ! decodebin ! videoconvert !  fakesink -v

QUIC_FPS.name: QUIC_FPS
QUIC_FPS.stream_server: gst-launch-1.0 -v filesrc location="/home/matt/Documents/zoom_recording.mp4" ! qtdemux name=demux  demux.video_0  ! rtph264pay ! quicsink host={addr} port=5000 log={lsquic_log}
QUIC_FPS.stream_client: gst-launch-1.0 quicsrc host={addr} port=5000 log={lsquic_log} caps="application/x-rtp, media=(string)video, clock-rate=(int)90000, encoding-name=(string)H264, payload=(int)96" ! rtpjitterbuffer latency={buffer_delay} ! rtph264depay ! queue ! h264parse ! decodebin ! videoconvert !  fakesink -v
